data.description: Welcome to your FULLY REMODELED Home! This large and beautiful 2 bed 2 bath ranch style townhome with an open basement and a 2 car garage has been freshly updated with new paint, new luxury vinyl flooring, new high end carpet & pad, new quartz countertops, new backsplash, new sinks and faucets, and new kitchen appliances!  Being located on the park & playground and at the community center it is a perfect place for entertaining.  As you enter the home you're welcomed with natural light flowing into the living room & dining room. Enjoy vaulted ceilings in the main living area and primary bedroom.  The updated kitchen will have you ready to cook a feast.  The Primary bedroom features a walk-in closet AND a second closet along with a spa inspired ensuite with new luxury vinyl flooring, new counters, a new sink & faucet.  The guest bedroom and bathroom are great additional living space. Main level laundry room is right off the 2 car garage entry.  And the large full unfinished basement is an added bonus if you ever wanted to expand.  Ample storage in the easy access crawl space.  Minutes to shopping, dining, entertainment & schools making it a perfect location! Hurry as this one will be gone fast!
